%% Diagram: CRDT library selection
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    A[Need collaborative<br/>data structure] --> B{Existing library<br/>fits the data shape?}
    B -->|Yes| C["Pick by runtime:<br/>JS/TS → Yjs or Automerge<br/>Rust+JS → Loro or Diamond Types<br/>JVM → Akka Distributed Data<br/>Erlang → riak_dt"]
    B -->|No| D{Team has<br/>CRDT depth?}
    D -->|No| I[Use a library anyway —<br/>CRDTs are subtle]
    D -->|Yes| J{Performance<br/>critical?}
    J -->|No| I
    J -->|Yes| K[Build custom +<br/>formal verification]
